Dear Hiring Team, 

It is with great pleasure that I submit my candidacy for the Staff Engineer position with Charles Schwab. I bring over three years of professional experience in full-stack web application development, distributed systems, and cloud-based microservices, along with a strong academic foundation as a Master of Science in Computer Science graduate from Pace University, NY.

