nce standards. I developed backend workflows using AWS Step Functions handling long-running data import jobs and preventing AWS Lambda timeouts, applying event-driven patterns and debugging methodologies ensuring reliability and responsiveness. Together, these roles have prepared me to design and develop scalable, high-performance web trading applications and contribute meaningfully to the Advisor Services Technology Web Trading team's core engineering responsibilities.

